1.title: Kat Tat - Grammy Weekend 2016 #ICYMI

episode of.title: Windi World Daily with Windi Washington (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: #ICYMI WINDI WORLD DAILY WITH WINDI WASHINGTON had an amazing time hanging out watching tattoo artist, painter and entrepreneur KAT TAT at Under The Gun Tattoo Co. on Melrose Avenue during Grammy Weekend 2016, while tattooing some of her Los Angeles fabulous clients. During my time spent with her, we discussed how she got her start in becoming a famous tattoo artist and what her future holds moving to Los Angeles.

2.title: Bernard Telsey, CSA - 31st Annual Artios Awards 2016 #ICYMI

episode of.title: Windi World Daily with Windi Washington (TV Series 2016– )

2.plot: #ICYMI WINDI WORLD DAILY with WINDI WASHINGTON interviewed Emmy-nominated Casting Director BERNARD TELSEY on the red carpet at the 31st Annual Artios Awards 2016. Casting Society of America honored him with the Hoyt Bowers Award for his Broadway and Off-Broadway casting career achievements.
